                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.516/110</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Saltillo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-12-22T18:00:00-06:41">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 22, 1915, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Matter of bank situation again discussed fully with First Chief this morning.
                    Unable to obtain any further expression than that conveyed in my December 21, 5
                    p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Silliman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
